---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Concierge Medicine in Wayne, PA | Forward Family Medicine"
  description="Forward Family Medicine offers concierge-style primary care on the Philadelphia Main Line — same-day access, direct physician contact, and unhurried visits — through an affordable DPC membership."
  canonical="https://www.forwardfamilymedicine.com/concierge-medicine"
>

  <!-- ─── Hero ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Wayne, PA · Philadelphia Main Line</p>
      <h1>Concierge Medicine in Wayne, PA</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">This is concierge medicine. The monthly fee just doesn't require a second mortgage. Every member gets same-day access, unhurried visits, and a physician whose panel is capped at 250 — structured on the Direct Primary Care model.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── What Is Concierge Medicine ───────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">What It Means</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">What Is Concierge Medicine?</h2>
      <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Concierge medicine (also called boutique medicine or retainer medicine) is an approach to primary care where patients pay a membership fee in exchange for enhanced access and a deeper relationship with their physician. The core promise is simple: <strong>a doctor with time for you.</strong></p>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">👥</span>
          <h3>Small Patient Panel</h3>
          <p>Your doctor knows you by name and history. At FFM, we cap our panel at 250 patients per physician — less than half the size of most DPC practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">⚡</span>
          <h3>Same-Day Access</h3>
          <p>Same-day availability for acute issues. Routine visits within 24 hours. Many questions resolved by phone or message — no visit required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">📱</span>
          <h3>Direct Physician Contact</h3>
          <p>Call or text your doctor directly. You will not reach an answering service, a nurse line, or a portal message that takes three days to answer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">⏱️</span>
          <h3>Visits Without a Clock</h3>
          <p>Appointments are scheduled to fit the conversation — not to hit a billing threshold. Complex visits get the time they need.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">🎯</span>
          <h3>Proactive Prevention</h3>
          <p>We don't wait for you to get sick. We schedule preventive reviews, track labs over time, and follow up on recommendations proactively.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">💰</span>
          <h3>Actively Lowers Your Costs</h3>
          <p>Wholesale lab pricing, medications at cost, and fewer urgent care visits. The goal: your total healthcare spend goes down as an FFM member.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Comparison Table ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">The Comparison</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">How Forward Family Medicine Compares</h2>
      <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">Traditional concierge medicine charges a premium retainer on top of — or instead of — insurance billing. DPC removes the insurance overhead entirely, which is what allows FFM to deliver the same concierge experience at a fraction of the cost.</p>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table class="compare-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Feature</th>
              <th class="col-trad">Traditional Concierge</th>
              <th class="col-ffm">Forward Family Medicine</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="row-feature">Patient panel size</td>
              <td class="col-trad">300–600 patients</td>
              <td class="col-ffm">~250 patients per physician</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="row-feature">Monthly cost</td>
              <td class="col-trad">$400+/month</td>
              <td class="col-ffm">$200/mo individual; family from $175 down to $100/person</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="row-feature">Insurance billing</td>
              <td class="col-trad">Often still billed</td>
              <td class="col-ffm">Never — no insurance billing for primary care</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="row-feature">Visit length</td>
              <td class="col-trad">30–60 minutes</td>
              <td class="col-ffm">1–2 hours</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="row-feature">Direct doctor access</td>
              <td class="col-trad">Yes</td>
              <td class="col-ffm">Yes — phone, text, email directly</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="row-feature">Lifestyle Medicine</td>
              <td class="col-trad">Rarely included</td>
              <td class="col-ffm">Board-eligible, in-person, every visit</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="table-footer-note">Same experience. Lower overhead. Better medicine. <a href="/direct-primary-care">Learn more about how DPC works →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── The Experience ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">The Difference</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The Concierge Experience at Forward Family Medicine</h2>
      <div class="experience-grid">
        <div class="experience-item">
          <h3>Your Doctor's Personal Attention</h3>
          <p>Dr. Bigley and Dr. Lieberman maintain a purposefully small panel of members. That means every patient receives the kind of attention that simply isn't possible in a practice seeing 20–30 patients a day.</p>
          <p>When you call, you speak directly with your doctor or a team member who knows your name. When you send a message, you receive a thoughtful response — not a portal notification pointing you back to schedule an appointment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="experience-item">
          <h3>A Practice That Actively Lowers Your Costs</h3>
          <p>Concierge medicine has a reputation for being expensive. We think it should be the opposite. Because we know you well and you can reach us directly, we help you avoid the urgent care visits, redundant tests, and reactive ER trips that quietly inflate the cost of traditional care.</p>
          <p>We dispense medications at cost and order labs at wholesale pricing — so when something is needed, it's not a financial event.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Who Benefits Most ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Who It's For</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Who Benefits Most from Concierge-Style DPC?</h2>
      <div class="persona-grid">
        <div class="persona-card">
          <span class="persona-icon">💼</span>
          <h3>Busy Professionals</h3>
          <p>When you can't afford to spend three hours waiting at urgent care, having same-day access to your own doctor — by phone, video, or in-person — changes everything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="persona-card">
          <span class="persona-icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</span>
          <h3>Families with Children</h3>
          <p>One membership covers a family. Having a physician who knows your children's history — and yours — makes routine and urgent care far simpler and more reassuring.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="persona-card">
          <span class="persona-icon">🩺</span>
          <h3>Adults with Chronic Conditions</h3>
          <p>Diabetes, hypertension, and thyroid disease require consistent, attentive management. The DPC model gives your doctor the time and continuity to manage these well.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="persona-card">
          <span class="persona-icon">💬</span>
          <h3>Anyone Who's Felt Rushed</h3>
          <p>If you've ever left a doctor's appointment feeling like your questions weren't answered, or like the visit ended before you could say everything — this practice was built for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Inline CTA ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="inline-cta">
        <h2>Experience Concierge-Style Care on the Main Line</h2>
        <p>Start with a free, no-obligation conversation. Meet the physicians, see the practice, and ask everything you want to know — with zero pressure.</p>
        <div class="inline-cta-btns">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent">Schedule a Free Meet &amp; Greet</a>
          <a href="/membership" class="btn btn-outline-white">See Membership Pricing →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Serving the Main Line ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container content-narrow">
      <span class="section-label">Serving the Philadelphia Main Line</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Wayne, PA and Surrounding Communities</h2>
      <p>Wayne, Pennsylvania is a vibrant Philadelphia Main Line community known for its walkable downtown, excellent schools, and family-friendly neighborhoods. Many residents choose personalized primary care that prioritizes prevention, longer visits, and strong doctor–patient relationships — which is the focus of Forward Family Medicine.</p>
      <p>We serve Wayne, Berwyn, Devon, Malvern, Paoli, Radnor, Villanova, Newtown Square, and surrounding communities.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── FAQ ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Common Questions</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Is concierge medicine worth it?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a" hidden>
            <p>Most patients who have experienced both traditional and concierge-style care say yes — particularly when the total cost (including copays, deductibles, and the value of time saved) is factored in. Our DPC model keeps the membership fee low enough that the math works for most families.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Does Forward Family Medicine bill insurance?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a" hidden>
            <p>We do not bill insurance for primary care services. Your monthly membership fee covers all included services. You should maintain health insurance for specialist, hospital, and emergency care.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>How small is the patient panel really?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a" hidden>
            <p>We keep our panel purposefully limited to ensure every member receives the attention they deserve. Once the panel is full, we maintain a waitlist. We encourage prospective members to <a href="/contact">reach out early →</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Can I keep my current insurance and add this membership?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a" hidden>
            <p>Yes. Most members combine our DPC membership with their existing insurance (or switch to a high-deductible plan) for specialist and hospital coverage.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>What if I want to keep my relationships with my current specialists?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a" hidden>
            <p>We work collaboratively with specialist physicians and large health systems. You do not need to abandon those relationships — you simply add a primary care physician who is far more accessible and engaged.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top:2rem; font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--ink-500);">More questions? <a href="/faq">See our full FAQ →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Bottom CTA ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="bottom-cta">
    <div class="container bottom-cta-inner">
      <div class="bottom-cta-text">
        <h2>Ready to Experience Medicine the Way It Should Be?</h2>
        <p>No commitment — just a conversation to see if it's the right fit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bottom-cta-btns">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent">Schedule a Free Meet &amp; Greet</a>
        <a href="/membership" class="btn btn-outline-white">See Membership Plans →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── Hero ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--green-500);
    padding: clamp(48px, 8vw, 80px) 0;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--green-200);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .page-hero h1 { color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .hero-desc {
    color: var(--green-100);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
    max-width: 700px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── Section alternates ──────────────────── */
  .section-alt { background: var(--cream-200); }

  /* ─── Feature grid ──────────────────────────── */
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .feature-card {
    background: var(--green-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--green-100);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--ink-700);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── Comparison table ──────────────────────── */
  .table-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-300);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .compare-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .compare-table thead th {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: none;
    background: var(--green-500);
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .compare-table thead th.col-trad {
    background: var(--warm-200);
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .compare-table thead th.col-ffm {
    background: var(--green-300);
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .compare-table tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-300); }
  .compare-table tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .compare-table td {
    padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
    border: none;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--cream-300);
  }
  .compare-table td:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .compare-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--warm-100); }
  .compare-table tbody tr td.col-ffm { background: var(--green-50); }
  .row-feature { font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-900); }
  .col-trad { color: var(--ink-500); }
  .col-ffm { color: var(--green-500); font-weight: 500; }
  .table-footer-note {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-500);
  }
  .table-footer-note a { color: var(--green-300); }

  /* ─── Experience section ────────────────────── */
  .experience-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .experience-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .experience-item p {
    color: var(--ink-700);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .experience-item p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ─── Persona grid ──────────────────────────── */
  .persona-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .persona-card {
    background: var(--warm-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--warm-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
  }
  .persona-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .persona-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .persona-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-700);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ─── Inline CTA ───────────────────────────── */
  .inline-cta {
    background: var(--green-500);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem) clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .inline-cta h2 { color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .inline-cta p {
    color: var(--green-100);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
  }
  .inline-cta-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* ─── Content narrow ────────────────────────── */
  .content-narrow { max-width: 760px; }
  .content-narrow p { color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .content-narrow p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ─── FAQ ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .faq-list { max-width: 800px; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-300); }
  .faq-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--cream-300); }
  .faq-q {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink-900);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .faq-q:hover { color: var(--green-400); }
  .faq-toggle {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--green-400);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .faq-q[aria-expanded="true"] .faq-toggle { transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .faq-a { padding-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .faq-a p { color: var(--ink-500); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0; }
  .faq-a a { color: var(--green-300); }

  /* ─── Bottom CTA ────────────────────────────── */
  .bottom-cta {
    background: var(--ink-900);
    padding: clamp(48px, 8vw, 80px) 0;
  }
  .bottom-cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .bottom-cta h2 { color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .bottom-cta p { color: var(--ink-300); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 480px; margin: 0; }
  .bottom-cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ─── Responsive ────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .experience-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .persona-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .bottom-cta-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-q').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const expanded = btn.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
      const answer = btn.nextElementSibling as HTMLElement;
      btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(!expanded));
      if (answer) answer.hidden = expanded;
    });
  });
</script>
